    <item>
      <title>[线性代数] 19.向量的内积&amp;长度&amp;正交</title>
      <link>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/19.%E5%90%91%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E7%A7%AF%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%A6%E6%AD%A3%E4%BA%A4/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 00:00:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>xxx@example.com (byzh)</author>
      <guid>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/19.%E5%90%91%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E7%A7%AF%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%A6%E6%AD%A3%E4%BA%A4/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[线性代数] 19.向量的内积&长度&正交</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h2 id="内积">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%86%85%e7%a7%af"></a>
内积
</h2><p>$[\alpha, \beta]$:</p>
<p><img src="/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/19.%E5%90%91%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E7%A7%AF%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%A6%E6%AD%A3%E4%BA%A4/image-20260705125742089.png" alt="image-20260705125742089"></p>
<h2 id="长度模范数">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e9%95%bf%e5%ba%a6%e6%a8%a1%e8%8c%83%e6%95%b0"></a>
长度/模/范数
</h2><p>$||\alpha||$:</p>
<p><img src="/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/19.%E5%90%91%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E7%A7%AF%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%A6%E6%AD%A3%E4%BA%A4/image-20260705130117270.png" alt="image-20260705130117270"></p>
<ul>
<li>$||\alpha||=1$ 则为单位向量</li>
<li>单位化: 把向量除以自己的范数 -&gt; 单位向量</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="正交">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e6%ad%a3%e4%ba%a4"></a>
正交
</h2><p>$\alpha$ 与 $\beta$ 正交（即 $\alpha \perp \beta$）$\iff [\alpha,\beta] = 0$</p>
<ul>
<li>若一个向量组的向量两两正交, 且均不为零向量, 则称为<strong>正交向量组</strong></li>
<li>若一个向量组的向量两两正交, 且均为单位向量, 则称为<strong>单位正交向量组</strong>/标准正交向量组/规范正交向量组</li>
</ul>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-07-05首发于<a href='https://byzhrichard.github.io/'>byzh的博客</a>，最后修改于2026-07-05</p>]]>
      </description>
      
        <category>线性代数</category>
      
    </item>
    
    

